@daxian-dbw 

File `https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/master/src/PowerShell.Core.Instrumentation/PowerShell.Core.Instrumentation.man` contains a number of occurrences of event log messages related to "Windows PowerShell ISE" and "PowerShell ISE".

